      "id": "PopularPost134393",
      "post_content": "Lots of flavor, and really great idea to combo with cumulative upkeep.   \n  \nAnd I agree, braid of fire as a snow permanent would have been awesome, and a very fair super-combo, I think. It couldn't win you the game, and it requires both cards and a you can't speed up braid of fire. Even so, I guess you COULD turn braid into a snow permanent. W/e, I still love Cover of Winter.",
